title.narrative: Support acceleration of geothermal development in Indonesia (GEo-INZ): Energy

description.narrative: This Activity will support geothermal energy development and access to energy in Indonesia through provision of technical assistance and capacity building to three Indonesian Partner agencies focused on geothermal development: Badan Geologi, the Directorate for New Energy, Renewable Energy and Energy (EBTKE), and PT Sarana Multi Infrastruktur (PT SMI).
